230
00:12:27,655 --> 00:12:31,155
kerana mereka tak kenal rupa saya, bukan?

231
00:12:32,395 --> 00:12:33,794
Ya, betul.

232
00:12:33,795 --> 00:12:36,294
Kami akan tiba di sana dalam sepuluh minit. Selamat tinggal.

233
00:12:36,295 --> 00:12:39,394
