235
00:12:41,295 --> 00:12:42,794
Terima kasih.

236
00:12:42,795 --> 00:12:45,794
Hei, saya ingat saya ialah bos kamu?

237
00:12:45,795 --> 00:12:49,094
Kamu ada kata apa-apa, pemandu?

238
00:12:49,095 --> 00:12:51,194
Adakah kamu tak rasa pelik?

239
00:12:51,195 --> 00:12:54,494
Mengapa budak Eisuke itu tiba-tiba hilang?

240
00:12:54,495 --> 00:12:58,894
