260
00:13:54,595 --> 00:13:56,294
Tak, salah!

261
00:13:56,295 --> 00:14:00,794
Kalau difikirkan, dia kata dia terjumpa satu petunjuk.

262
00:14:00,795 --> 00:14:03,094
